I agree with @amychomd - we need all available doses of #COVID19 given quickly & efficiently without “stops” for weekends/holidays!
We need 24/7/365 ongoing vaccination.
Each day #vaccine sits in a freezer is another day SARsCoV2 infects & spreads, & lives are lost.
